# Copy to ".env" in the project root (see README). Never commit real values.
#
# On IPv4-only networks, **db.<ref>.supabase.co** often fails DNS (Windows 11001). Use the **Session pooler**
# string from Supabase → Connect (user **postgres.<ref>**, host **aws-0-** or **aws-1-**… — copy host exactly).
# (Tokyo is often **ap-northeast-1**; pooler may be **aws-1-…**, not aws-0.)

# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres.YOUR_REF:URL_ENCODED_PASSWORD@aws-1-ap-northeast-1.pooler.supabase.com:5432/postgres?sslmode=require
# SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_REF.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_KEY=your_key_here
